rows.label: qst640402_msg0001
rows.name: That's...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0002
rows.name: A win, isn't it?

rows.label: qst640402_msg0003
rows.name: It says "first prize", right here.

rows.label: qst640402_msg0004
rows.name: F-f-f-fi... First prize?!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0005
rows.name: That very not possible!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0006
rows.name:
Gachagacha take first prize out of
prize pool himself...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0007
rows.name:
Whatever, guy. The first prize is the
first prize! It's what the thing says!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0008
rows.name: Or are you saying Kasane cheated?

rows.label: qst640402_msg0009
rows.name:
B-but... If friend truly win first prize,
then Gachagacha go out of business...
Lose earnings and also savings!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0010
rows.name:
For sure, a free pass to the Superbia
hot springs sounds like it would cost
a pretty penny...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0011
rows.name:
And yet, a win is a win, is it not?
You should have thought of that
before you started your hustle, peon.

rows.label: qst640402_msg0012
rows.name:
We will be having our prize, or else
we will be having your head.
Which one will it be?

rows.label: qst640402_msg0013
rows.name: ...Choice is fairly obvious, meh...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0014
rows.name:
Not hand over prize also mean loss
of any remaining credibility as
independent raffle operator...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0015
rows.name:
Maybe you should have chosen
another business to get into...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0016
rows.name:
No more business to do here...
Gachagacha go be somewhere
else now...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0017
rows.name: You have a great day now!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0018
rows.name:
Such an achievement, Kasane!
We are so proud of you, oh most
beloved of friends!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0019
rows.name: Is that right...?

rows.label: qst640402_msg0020
rows.name:
A lifetime of free entry to the
Superbia bathhouse! Oh, be still
our beating heart!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0021
rows.name:
I feel bad pointing this out, but aren't
you basically spending your lifetime
in a bathtub anyway...?

rows.label: qst640402_msg0022
rows.name: That is not the point!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0023
rows.name:
We wish to bathe together with you,
dearest Kasane, and the rest of our
entourage, as we sip tea and exult!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0024
rows.name:
And you, surely you must wish the
same wish as we! For why else would
you have entered the raffle?

rows.label: qst640402_msg0025
rows.name: No, I don't think I did...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0026
rows.name:
I just kinda hoped something nice
would happen for everyone!
Same as always!

rows.label: qst640402_msg0027
rows.name: Mgghhh...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0028
rows.name:
Someone doesn't seem to see it
that way...

rows.label: qst640402_msg0029
rows.name:
Ah, whatever. Hot springs sound really
good right now! Shall we head for
Superbia, then?
